    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Alchemists's Supplies boost your spell!</p>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Full Description</strong></summary>\n<blockquote style=\"font-style:normal\">\n<p>At 5th level, you've developed masterful command of magical chemicals, enhancing the healing and damage you create through them. Whenever you cast a spell using your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-items.JK0OX6MAQvfpdSAw]{Alchemist's Supplies} as the spellcasting focus, you gain a bonus to one roll of the spell. That roll must restore hit points or be a damage roll that deals <strong>acid</strong>, <strong>fire</strong>, <strong>necrotic</strong>, or <strong>poison damage</strong>, and the bonus equals your <strong>Intelligence modifier</strong> (minimum of +1).</p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>",
